Due to the nature of our nonprofit entity (the clients we will serve), I was asked by the insurance carrier if we had anti-harassment and anti-discrimination policies. Although we had all the other necessary policies, it never dawned on us that those were the two most valuable pieces every organization (not just a nonprofit) must be in possession of.
Since I’ve worked with this seller before (who does awesome work), I immediately reached out to obtain her services. And that’s because I’m familiar with the quality of her work and the level of her skills. The language she uses in these policies is so detailed and polished. It is obvious she has a thorough legal background and is familiar with the language a company document must contain (under the legalities of their state law).


I wasn’t just impressed with the presentation of her work, but the quick turnaround was an extra, extra, extra plus. No kidding, it was amazing! You go to sleep, you wake up, and BAM, there it is—right in your box, ready and waiting for approval! That’s what I call “top-notch service.” I must say, “This girl is bad.” And I mean bad in a good way. Her work ethics are outstanding. Certainly, she knows her stuff and won’t keep you waiting for what is expected.

There are some acquaintances I know we are starting and/or have started their nonprofit; rest assured, this will be one seller’s name I will be kicking around for their business needs. People, if you are in need of these specialty services, do not hesitate—I repeat, “Do not hesitate to reach out to her and utilize her services.” I want each of you to remember this seller and her business name (i.e., Rohn), @rohanmaqbool. I have no doubt you’ll be a repeat customer as well. Don’t just take my word for it. Check her out, and you can thank me later!


Rohn (seller), “I’m so pleased to have found you on this site (Fiverr.com).” Continue to do what you do. You are awesome!
Simply amazing experience! very professional and patient to understand exactly what's needed. I feel like I have a virtual legal profession on my team. thanks for your impactful assistance
